  [Text] Seoul, April 27 (YONHAP) -- The foreign ministers of 
South Korea and Cote d'Ivoire met Wednesday for talks on 
promoting bilateral relations and cooperation in the 
international arena. 
  Han Sung-chu greeted his counterpart Amara Essy at the 
Foreign Ministry and exchanged opinions on recent developments 
on the Korean peninsula and in Africa, officials said. The two 
