to Vietcom Bank to facilitate Korean exports to Vietnam. Exim 
Bank Governor Chae Hong-sik and Vietcom Bank Vice President Ha 
Hui-song signed a contract Wednesday for the relending service 
covering three to 10 years and carrying annual interest rates of 
