<H4>    Received by Foreign Minister </H4>

<F P=102> BK0305105094 Vientiane KPL in English 0901 GMT 3 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK0305105094 </F>
<F P=104>  Vientiane KPL </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Vientiane, May 3 (KPL) -- Foreign Minister Somsavat 
Lengsavat yesterday received visiting German State Secetary and 
Deputy Miister for Economic Cooperation and Develoqment, Wighard 
Hardte. 
  The Lao foreign minister, talking with the German economic 
cooperation delegation, has contributed towards developing the 
good relations of friendship and cooperation between Laos and 
Germany. He highly appreciated the growing cooperation between 
the two countries as well as the German assistance to Laos. 
  In response, Wighard Hardte thanked Somsavath Lengsavat for 
extending him a warm welcome during his visit to the country. He 
confirmed that the German Government has agreed to give 
assistance to Laos in such areas as education and human 
resources development. 
  In the morning of the same day, the German deputy minister 
met with Acting Minister of Finance Bounlit Khenavong. 

