  [Text] Pyongyang, April 30 (KCNA) -- The dear leader 
Comrade Kim Chong-il sent thanks to many units and working 
people who had actively helped in the construction of grand 
monumental edifices including the monument to the victory in the 
fatherland liberation war. They include the North Pyongan 
