<H3> <TI>   DPRK Reaffirms Position of No Sample-Taking </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    DPRK Reaffirms Position of No Sample-Taking </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0405034294 Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network in Korean 0310 GMT 4 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK0405034294 </F>
<F P=104>  Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Korean </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The International Atomic Energy Agency [IAEA] on 4 
May disclosed that North Korea has reaffirmed its stance of not 
