<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    U.S., ROK Conduct Military Exercise 3 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0505050194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0438 GMT 5 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0505050194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 5 (KCNA) -- Pacific-based U.S. F-15 
fighter bombers, FA-18 pursuit-assault planes and warplanes of 
other types and warplanes of the U.S. Airforce in South Korea 
and the puppet Airforce, over 450 in all, staged a military 
exercise against the North in the sky above the area near the 
Military Demarcation Line on May 3, according to military 
sources. 
  Meanwhile, tanks of the South Korean puppet Army deployed in 
Kumpa-ri, Paju County, fired about 20 shells at Hapo-ri of the 
same county and large-calibre gun units that had taken position 
in Mago-ri of Yonchon County, Yongsan-ri of Paju County, and 
Yulli-ri of Chorwon County of South Korean Kangwon Province 
fired some 70 shells into the area adjacent to the Demilitarized 
Zone. 
  The war moves of the U.S. imperialists and the South Korean 
puppets getting more wanton prove that they are rushing toward 
confrontation and war, going against peace and detente in Korea. 

</TEXT>

