BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 30 (KCNA) -- The Zimbabwean 
Committee for the Repatriation of Kim In-so and Ham Se-hwan to 
the North was inaugurated in Harare on April 20. 
  Parliamentarian J. Macheka, secretary of the Zimbabwe-Korea 
