<H3> <TI>   Chongnyon Delegation, Visiting Groups Arrive </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Chongnyon Delegation, Visiting Groups Arrive </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0305214394 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1521 GMT 3 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0305214394 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 3 (KCNA) -- A delegation of officials 
of the General Association of Korean Residents in Japan 
(Chongnyon) led by Kim Su-chin, a department director of 
Chongnyon Central Standing Committee, and a home-visiting group 
of Korean students in Japan and the 211th short-term 
home-visiting group of Koreans in Japan arrived in Wonsan Monday 
by the ship "Mangyongbong-92" for a visit to the socialist 
motherland. 

</TEXT>

