  Addressing the inaugural meeting, the chairman of the 
preparatory committee for the inauguration of the society said: 
  The immortal chuche idea founded by respected President Kim 
Il-song is being further developed and enriched by His 
Excellency Kim Chong-il. The chuche idea is a guiding idea of 
revolution and a banner of struggle to realize independence of 
the popular masses. 
  He said all people who espouse the chuche idea deem it their 
supreme desire to have the august name of His Excellency Kim 
Chong-il, and stressed the need to learn from him and deeply 
study his works. 
  Messages of greetings to the great leader President Kim 
Il-song and the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il were adopted 
