<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Establishes New District in Kon Tum </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0305142894 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 
1430 GMT 1 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0305142894 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network </F>
<F P=105>  Vietnamese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Summary] On 24 March [date as heard], the government 
issued Decree No. 29 on establishing Dac Ha District of Kon Tum 
Province. The district was established on the basis of 
incorporating two villages of Dac To and Dac Lay with four 
villages of Kon Tum city. 
  Dac Ha has almost 75,000 hectares of natural land and a 
population of more than 29,800. It has seven administrative 
units. 

</TEXT>

